_360_NON_GAME"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": null, "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["TOUCHPAD"], "supported_player_modes": [], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "4861922570528321"}, "review_messages": ["Hi,\n\nThanks for letting us know.  We will go ahead remove the old app from the store and release your new one today.  Thanks for letting us know.", "Hi,\n\nThanks for reaching out.  We reached out via email and did notice that you have two apps that are exactly the same.  Instead of taking down the original app making a new one, we require that you update your old one instead.", "", "Congratulations! Your submission is ready to publish in the Oculus Store.  \n\nBefore your release we require that you update your assets.  Your assets currently look like screenshots and don't portray what your app does.  Please reconsider the style and design of your assets.  If you need guidance on what assets should look like, please use this as a reference: https://static.oculus.com/documents/oculus-store-art-guidelines.pdf.  In addition, screenshot 4 is not screen shot, please submit something different.\n\nPlease provide new assets by 6/19/2018 so your app will can be released on 6/20/2018 @ 10am PT under the Apps Section of the Mobile store. Also do not update your online services (such as your back-end servers) during your launch week.\n\nOnce your submission is published, you can access analytics [here](https://developer.oculus.com/apps/). ", ""]}]}, "cover_square_image": {"uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/12386220_1086781434804011_2193209940007452672_n.png?stp=dst-png_s360x360&_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=ADGS-BR4X4kQ7kNvgHvM2Tp&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDJzX0Wc0YCXYa406ME_CzH-GFDvtnfOHGh3uD